snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK Vol. 3 Trailer
snippet.description: Fans of Cookie Masterson rejoice! This is his first volume as full-time host -- the game that launched a "career," if you can call it that! The spawning continues as the award-winning YOU DON'T KNOW JACK series pumps out YOU DON'T KNOW JACK Volume 3.
